== 229. defer ordering in complex nesting
----------------------------------------------------------------

-- Multiple defers in one scope (LIFO)
  enter
  body
  defer C
  defer B
  defer A

-- Defer in nested scopes (inner scope first)
  outer body before inner
    inner body
    inner defer
  outer body after inner
  outer defer

-- Defer in nested if blocks
  inside if positive
  inside very-positive
  very positive defer
  back to positive scope
  positive defer
  outer continues
  outer defer (n=5)

-- Defer in a loop body fires every iteration
    body iteration 0
    defer iteration 0 done
    body iteration 1
    defer iteration 1 done
    body iteration 2
    defer iteration 2 done

