== 400. FormatInt: bases and widths
----------------------------------------------------------------
default base 10        : 255
base 2  min 8          : 11111111
base 8  min 4          : 0377
base 16 min 4          : 00ff
base 16 min 8          : 000000ff
base 16 min 2          : ff

-- Custom padding character
space-padded width 6   : [    42]
star -padded width 6   : [****42]
undr-padded width 6    : [____42]

-- Minimum digits less than actual digits (no truncation)
100000 min 2           : 100000
100000 min 0           : 100000
100000 min 1           : 100000

----------------------------------------------------------------
== 401. FormatInt: digits_per_comma and comma_string
----------------------------------------------------------------
default                : 1234567890
commas every 3 with ',': 1,234,567,890
commas every 3 with '_': 1_234_567_890
commas every 4 with ' ': 12 3456 7890
commas every 2 with '.': 12.34.56.78.90

-- Commas with hex and binary
hex every 4 with '_'   : dead_beef
hex every 2 with ':'   : de:ad:be:ef
bin every 4 with '|'   : 1100|1010
bin every 8 with ' '   : 11001010 11111110

-- Negative numbers with commas
negative commas        : -1,000,000

----------------------------------------------------------------
== 402. FormatInt: negative numbers in each base
----------------------------------------------------------------
base 10                : -42
base 2  width 16       : 1111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111010110
base 8  width 8        : 1777777777777777777726
base 16 width 8        : ffffffffffffffd6


-- Big negative
base 10                : -9000000000
base 10 commas         : -9,000,000,000

