== 513. Tower of Hanoi move sequence
----------------------------------------------------------------
  3-disk solution has 7 moves:
    step 1: disk 1 from peg 1 to peg 3
    step 2: disk 2 from peg 1 to peg 2
    step 3: disk 1 from peg 3 to peg 2
    step 4: disk 3 from peg 1 to peg 3
    step 5: disk 1 from peg 2 to peg 1
    step 6: disk 2 from peg 2 to peg 3
    step 7: disk 1 from peg 1 to peg 3
  4-disk solution has 15 moves
  5-disk solution has 31 moves

