== 751. Nested defer through function return
----------------------------------------------------------------
call with i=0
  outer_body n=0
    inner_defer for n=0
  outer_defer for n=0
got back v=1
call with i=1
  outer_body n=1
    inner_body n=1
    inner_defer for n=1
  outer_defer for n=1
got back v=2
call with i=2
  outer_body n=2
    inner_body n=2
    inner_defer for n=2
  outer_defer for n=2
got back v=3
call with i=3
  outer_body n=3
    inner_body n=3
    inner_defer for n=3
  outer_defer for n=3
got back v=4
call with i=4
  outer_body n=4
    inner_body n=4
    inner_defer for n=4
  outer_defer for n=4
got back v=5

